---
title: Indian Sheet Pan Chicken and Cauliflower with Pilau Rice and Lime Yogurt
description: Yogurt plays double-duty in this Indian feast! Mixed some of the yogurt with ginger and spices as a quick marinade for chicken and mix the rest with cucumber to make raita for cooling richness.
